181
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,470
Ryu!

182
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:31,780
- Ryu! 
 - Ei!

183
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:33,560
Ryu?

184
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,520
